00090098 - **醫療資訊概論  Medical information management, Fall  2009











Medical information management
醫療資訊概論
Instructor:
簡文山
Wen-Shan Jian
College of Medicine
Taipei Medical University
Course Structure: 2 hour per a week
 TMU Podcast 播客





Image courtesy of eduCommons (275px x 275px)
Course Description
This course will introduce: -Hosipital Information System -Medical Informatics Coding and Classification -The Patient Record -Medical Imaging -Medical Knowledge and Decision Support -Medical Informatics Standard
從醫療院所之組織功能、政府政策面入手，介紹資訊的種類、標準、規劃、處理及分析，再引伸至資訊系統的設計、測試、驗收與維護，最後再論述醫療院所各項系統運作的實務。


開課系所:醫務管理學系
開課年級: 3
學分:2







